Racial identity politics is a mess. This show gets to the heart of race and what it means for us today. The aim of ‘Let’s Start an Argument’ is to spark rational argument around this controversial topic. Your hosts are Cecelia Kok and Dr Jason Werbeloff. They are hugely grateful to Advocate Mark Oppenheimer for his invaluable contribution to this podcast series. This is the fourth in a series of five podcasts.  Previous podcasts in the series: Let’s Start an Argument (I): The nature of race The Let's Start an Argument Podcast (II): Power in racial identity politics The Let's Start an Argument podcast (III): Race and one’s experience of the world   